# Data files (IMPORTANT!)
#########################
# Generally, you should NOT commit raw or large processed data files to Git.
# Version control for data is a separate, more complex topic (e.g., DVC, Git LFS).
# Small sample data for testing or demonstration might be an exception.
data/*
!data/.gitkeep  # Keep the directory structure if desired

!data/raw_data/
data/raw_data/*
!data/raw_data/.gitkeep

!data/processed_data/
data/processed_data/*
!data/processed_data/.gitkeep

external_data/
notebooks/data/ # if you store data directly inside notebooks folder

